{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":417,"text":"In an age of global strife\nand climate change,"},{"time":3644,"text":"I'm here to answer\nthe all important question:"},{"time":7130,"text":"Why is sex so damn good?"},{"time":10225,"text":"If you're laughing, you know what I mean."}]},{"cues":[{"time":12202,"text":"Now, before we get to that answer,"},{"time":14064,"text":"let me tell you about Chris Hosmer."},{"time":16282,"text":"Chris is a great friend of mine\nfrom my university days,"},{"time":18973,"text":"but secretly, I hate him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":21837,"text":"Here's why. Back in university,\nwe had a quick project"},{"time":24757,"text":"to design some solar-powered clocks."},{"time":26739,"text":"Here's my clock."},{"time":28293,"text":"It uses something called\nthe dwarf sunflower,"},{"time":30770,"text":"which grows to about 12 inches in height."},{"time":33116,"text":"Now, as you know, sunflowers"},{"time":35182,"text":"track the sun\nduring the course of the day."},{"time":37418,"text":"So in the morning, you see\nwhich direction the sunflower is facing,"},{"time":40780,"text":"and you mark it on the blank\narea in the base."},{"time":43970,"text":"At noon, you mark the changed\nposition of the sunflower,"},{"time":46921,"text":"and in the evening again,\nand that's your clock."},{"time":50293,"text":"Now, I know my clock doesn't\ntell you the exact time,"},{"time":52879,"text":"but it does give you a general\nidea using a flower."},{"time":55607,"text":"So, in my completely unbiased,\nsubjective opinion,"},{"time":58723,"text":"it's brilliant."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60442,"text":"However, here's Chris's clock."},{"time":63268,"text":"It's five magnifying glasses\nwith a shot glass under each one."},{"time":67319,"text":"In each shot glass\nis a different scented oil."},{"time":70240,"text":"In the morning, the sunlight\nwill shine down"},{"time":71759,"text":"on the first magnifying glass,"},{"time":73418,"text":"focusing a beam of light\non the shot glass underneath."},{"time":76448,"text":"This will warm up the scented oil inside,"},{"time":78647,"text":"and a particular smell will be emitted."},{"time":81231,"text":"A couple of hours later,\nthe sun will shine"},{"time":83303,"text":"on the next magnifying glass,\nand a different smell will be emitted."},{"time":86600,"text":"So during the course of the day,\nfive different smells"},{"time":89281,"text":"are dispersed throughout that environment."},{"time":91316,"text":"Anyone living in that house\ncan tell the time"},{"time":94056,"text":"just by the smell."},{"time":96528,"text":"You can see why I hate Chris."},{"time":98881,"text":"I thought my idea was pretty good,"},{"time":100525,"text":"but his idea is genius,"},{"time":102916,"text":"and at the time, I knew\nhis idea was better than mine,"},{"time":105537,"text":"but I just couldn't explain why."}]},{"cues":[{"time":108359,"text":"One thing you have to know\nabout me is I hate to lose."},{"time":111889,"text":"This problem's been bugging me\nfor well over a decade."},{"time":115751,"text":"All right, let's get back\nto the question of why sex is so good."},{"time":119111,"text":"Many years after the solar\npowered clocks project,"},{"time":121972,"text":"a young lady I knew suggested\nmaybe sex is so good"},{"time":125676,"text":"because of the five senses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127616,"text":"And when she said this, I had an epiphany."},{"time":130425,"text":"So I decided to evaluate different\nexperiences I had in my life"},{"time":134156,"text":"from the point of view of the five senses."},{"time":136644,"text":"To do this, I devised something\ncalled the five senses graph."},{"time":140354,"text":"Along the y-axis, you have\na scale from zero to 10,"},{"time":143439,"text":"and along the x-axis, you have,\nof course, the five senses."},{"time":146786,"text":"Anytime I had a memorable\nexperience in my life,"},{"time":149370,"text":"I would record it on this graph\nlike a five senses diary."},{"time":153365,"text":"Here's a quick video\nto show you how it works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156557,"text":"(Video) Jinsop Lee: Hey, my name's Jinsop,"},{"time":159373,"text":"and today, I'm going to show\nyou what riding motorbikes"},{"time":162017,"text":"is like from the point of view\nof the five senses. Hey!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":165302,"text":"Bike designer: This is [unclear],\ncustom bike designer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168908,"text":"(Motorcyle revving)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":174731,"text":"[Sound]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":195119,"text":"[Touch]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":204750,"text":"[Sight]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":215686,"text":"[Smell]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":223301,"text":"[Taste]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":229037,"text":"JL: And that's how the five senses\ngraph works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231962,"text":"Now, for a period of three years,\nI gathered data,"},{"time":235311,"text":"not just me but also some of my friends,"},{"time":238067,"text":"and I used to teach\nin university, so I forced my --"},{"time":240568,"text":"I mean, I asked my students\nto do this as well."},{"time":243253,"text":"So here are some other results."},{"time":245883,"text":"The first is for instant noodles."},{"time":248120,"text":"Now obviously, taste\nand smell are quite high,"},{"time":251180,"text":"but notice sound is at three."},{"time":255299,"text":"Many people told me a big part"},{"time":256875,"text":"of the noodle-eating experience\nis the slurping noise."},{"time":259897,"text":"You know. (Slurps)"},{"time":262279,"text":"Needless to say, I no longer\ndine with these people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265098,"text":"OK, next, clubbing."},{"time":267435,"text":"OK, here what I found interesting was"},{"time":271156,"text":"that taste is at four,\nand many respondents told me"},{"time":275825,"text":"it's because of the taste of drinks,"},{"time":277564,"text":"but also, in some cases, kissing is a big\npart of the clubbing experience."},{"time":281985,"text":"These people I still do hang out with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":284793,"text":"All right, and smoking."},{"time":287137,"text":"Here I found touch is at [six],\nand one of the reasons"},{"time":292184,"text":"is that smokers told me the sensation\nof holding a cigarette"},{"time":295540,"text":"and bringing it up to your lips is a big\npart of the smoking experience,"},{"time":299237,"text":"which shows, it's kind of scary to think"},{"time":301916,"text":"how well cigarettes are designed\nby the manufacturers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":305126,"text":"OK. Now, what would the perfect\nexperience"},{"time":308507,"text":"look like on the five senses graph?"},{"time":310986,"text":"It would, of course, be\na horizontal line along the top."},{"time":314507,"text":"Now you can see, not\neven as intense an experience"},{"time":317087,"text":"as riding a motorbike comes close."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319320,"text":"In fact, in the years\nthat I gathered data,"},{"time":321862,"text":"only one experience came close\nto being the perfect one."},{"time":325100,"text":"That is, of course, sex. Great sex."},{"time":328725,"text":"Respondents said that great sex"},{"time":330414,"text":"hits all of the five senses\nat an extreme level."}]},{"cues":[{"time":334269,"text":"Here I'll quote\none of my students who said,"},{"time":336389,"text":"\"Sex is so good, it's good\neven when it's bad.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":340626,"text":"So the five senses\ntheory does help explain"},{"time":343939,"text":"why sex is so good."},{"time":346056,"text":"Now in the middle of all this\nfive senses work,"},{"time":348905,"text":"I suddenly remembered\nthe solar-powered clocks project"},{"time":351714,"text":"from my youth."},{"time":352791,"text":"And I realized this theory\nalso explains why Chris's clock"},{"time":355783,"text":"is so much better than mine."},{"time":357664,"text":"You see, my clock only focuses on sight,"},{"time":360793,"text":"and a little bit of touch."},{"time":363231,"text":"Here's Chris's clock."},{"time":365214,"text":"It's the first clock ever\nthat uses smell to tell the time."},{"time":369863,"text":"In fact, in terms of the five senses,"},{"time":371929,"text":"Chris's clock is a revolution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374942,"text":"And that's what this theory\ntaught me about my field."},{"time":377580,"text":"You see, up till now, us designers,"},{"time":379479,"text":"we've mainly focused on making\nthings look very pretty,"},{"time":382485,"text":"and a little bit of touch,"},{"time":384281,"text":"which means we've ignored\nthe other three senses."},{"time":387460,"text":"Chris's clock shows us\nthat even raising just one"},{"time":389930,"text":"of those other senses can\nmake for a brilliant product."},{"time":393330,"text":"So what if we started using\nthe five senses theory"},{"time":397361,"text":"in all of our designs?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":398596,"text":"Here's three quick ideas I came up with."},{"time":401321,"text":"This is an iron, you\nknow, for your clothes,"},{"time":403924,"text":"to which I added a spraying mechanism,"},{"time":406693,"text":"so you fill up the vial\nwith your favorite scent,"},{"time":409244,"text":"and your clothes will smell nicer,"},{"time":411112,"text":"but hopefully it should also make"},{"time":412708,"text":"the ironing experience more enjoyable."},{"time":414716,"text":"We could call this \"the perfumator.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":417888,"text":"All right, next."},{"time":419373,"text":"So I brush my teeth twice a day,"},{"time":421416,"text":"and what if we had a toothbrush"},{"time":423822,"text":"that tastes like candy,"},{"time":425518,"text":"and when the taste of candy ran out,"},{"time":427993,"text":"you'd know it's time\nto change your toothbrush?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":430953,"text":"Finally, I have a thing for the keys\non a flute or a clarinet."},{"time":435532,"text":"It's not just the way they look,\nbut I love the way they feel"},{"time":438958,"text":"when you press down on them."},{"time":441188,"text":"Now, I don't play the flute\nor the clarinet,"},{"time":443328,"text":"so I decided to combine these keys\nwith an instrument I do play:"},{"time":447464,"text":"the television remote control."}]},{"cues":[{"time":450675,"text":"Now, when we look at these\nthree ideas together,"},{"time":453967,"text":"you'll notice that the five senses theory"},{"time":456887,"text":"doesn't only change the way\nwe use these products"},{"time":459891,"text":"but also the way they look."},{"time":462710,"text":"So in conclusion, I've found\nthe five senses theory"},{"time":466762,"text":"to be a very useful tool in evaluating"},{"time":469323,"text":"different experiences in my life,"},{"time":470919,"text":"and then taking those best experiences"},{"time":473867,"text":"and hopefully incorporating\nthem into my designs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":476515,"text":"Now, I realize the five senses\nisn't the only thing"},{"time":480432,"text":"that makes life interesting."},{"time":482350,"text":"There's also the six emotions"},{"time":484569,"text":"and that elusive x-factor."},{"time":488133,"text":"Maybe that could be\nthe topic of my next talk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491883,"text":"Until then, please have fun"},{"time":494292,"text":"using the five senses in your own lives"},{"time":496691,"text":"and your own designs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":498411,"text":"Oh, one last thing before I leave."},{"time":501196,"text":"Here's the experience you\nall had while listening"},{"time":503506,"text":"to the TED Talks."},{"time":504755,"text":"However, it would be better\nif we could boost up"},{"time":507067,"text":"a couple of the other senses\nlike smell and taste."},{"time":510731,"text":"And the best way to do that is with"},{"time":513783,"text":"free candy."},{"time":515436,"text":"You guys ready?"},{"time":517179,"text":"All right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":520504,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}